In order to enter "Hello" on the translation page, first click the text box to activate it, and then enter the text to be translated. The following is the action plan for completing this task:```json
[
    {"action_type": "MouseAction", "mouse_action_type": "click", "mouse_button": "left", "mouse_position": {"width": 400, "height": 400}},
    {"action_type": "KeyboardAction", "keyboard_action_type": "text", "keyboard_text": "\u4f60\u597d"}
]
```This operation plan first activates the central position of the text input box by left clicking, and then enters the text "Hello".
